➜《徽州夜市》（七绝十首）作者/杨克强
http://www.sohu.com/a/416652748_804243	51091
<p class="ql-align-center">《徽州夜市》（七绝十首）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 文/杨克强 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长街无处不霓虹，小吃香飘夜色中。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">涮罢成都麻辣烫，舌尖犹带蜀江风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百家餐馆接长龙，谁把唐街作美容。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一夜开张连日火，食材出自白云峰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来自巴山明月窗，青泥豆腐嫩无双。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">厨娘不识乡愁味，只是逢人夸蜀江。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白发阿婆厨艺奇，漏瓢做粉细如丝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乌鸡汤煮巴山月，正是游人畅饮时。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200905/96b3ab861b8443918636516464316e49.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">五</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">奶茶鲜果两清微，满座游人尽忘归。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">线上订单如雪片，送餐车载劲歌飞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">六</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">剪裁锡纸巧包鱼，香透桥南一品居。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打酒谁家妙龄女？桃花人面映霞裾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">七</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金风吹旺紫泥炉，陶罐熬成味道殊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">茶遇山泉汤色酽，一杯醉我胜屠苏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200905/86199b3196f147b093e00c7ebb9eae97.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁将土豆捣成泥，晨采鲜椒过柳堤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一碗乡愁百重味，昨宵又梦米仓西。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">九</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">听雨轩连品月斋，巴山风味老招牌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谪仙闲跨青崖鹿，畅饮淳醪醉四街。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">十</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夜市开张时正秋，百家酒馆并茶楼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嫦娥新烙桂花饼，摆个地摊忙不休。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200905/7a700bb011a9444d9e659475df022935.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>作者简介</p>
<p>杨克强，徽县人民法院副院长。中华诗词学会会员，甘肃省诗词学会第五届理事会理事、会员，听花榭会员，徽县诗歌学会秘书长。诗词作品散见于《中华诗词》《飞天》《甘肃诗词》《彭城诗派》等刊物。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200905/3aaefcba53cc40a59fc1352942cb9f56.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>来源：徽县人大办</p>
